# 🛒 My E-commerce Website

Welcome to my **E-commerce Website Project** inspired by platforms like Meesho!  
This project is part of my full-stack web development journey.

## 🚀 Features

- User-friendly UI using **HTML, CSS, JavaScript**
- Product listing page
- Add to cart functionality
- Responsive design
- Clean and modern layout

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- Replit (for development)
- Git & GitHub (for version control)

